milestones.description: This is the lowest match aggregate (497) involving teams U.A.E. & Afghanistan in ODIs
Khurram Khan has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (8) for UAE, going past Azhar Saeed
Samiullah Shinwari has scored 7 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for AFG breaking Mohammad Nabi's record
Dawlat Zadran has broken the record for most ducks (3) in ODIs for AFG, going past Shapoor's 3
Mohammad Nabi has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (38) for AFG, going past Samiullah Shinwari
